      <title>美元因利率前景而走强，油价扩大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-extends-losses-early-asian-trade-2024-02-26/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一油价下跌，延续前一交易日的跌幅，因市场担心高于预期的通胀可能会推迟美国高利率的下调，而高利率一直限制了全球燃料需求的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-extends-losses-early-asian-trade-2024-02-26/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 01:45:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
